01:13:59.600 --> 01:14:04.319
So your web applications, your printer reports, your dashboards, your presentations

01:14:04.319 --> 01:14:13.120
would all have a consistent look and feel. Brand YAML is relatively new. Right now it is supported

01:14:13.120 --> 01:14:21.040
in Cordo version 1.6 and above for the specific formats of HTML, Dashboard, Reveal.js, and Typed,

01:14:21.759 --> 01:14:27.759
all formats that we've talked about, coincidentally. It also is supported in Shiny for Python.

